# Exclude build artifacts, generated code, and third-party bundles
# from GitHub's language detection and diff view.

# Gradle caches & outputs
**/.gradle/** linguist-vendored
**/.gradle/** linguist-generated
**/build/** linguist-generated
**/.idea/** linguist-vendored

# CMake / NDK build artifacts
**/.cxx/** linguist-generated
**/cmake-build-*/** linguist-generated
**/CMakeFiles/** linguist-generated

# iOS derived data
**/DerivedData/** linguist-generated
**/Pods/** linguist-vendored

# Node / JS
**/node_modules/** linguist-vendored
**/dist/** linguist-generated
**/coverage/** linguist-generated

# Docs
docs/** linguist-documentation
*.md linguist-documentation=false
